Flow:

Install nginx
  * use official ansible role
    * Set up nginx conf file

Configure system for nginx
  * Get SSL keys working
  * open up required port(s)
  * any additional hardening (f2b?)

Download apollo_api code from gitup

Install the requirements.txt file via pip (gunicorn, sqlalchemy, requests, sanction, etc)

Install the apollo_api project

initialize database (if not already initialized)
  * Perhaps do database initialization as a separate play/role?
  
Launch project
  * start nginx
  * start gunicorn

Run tests


